Having got acquainted with the car, the French specialists began its preparation for the start in the Paris-Dakar marathon in 1978. The two Niva declared by J.-J. , speaking on these cars and prototypes with the name "Niva", managed to take third place, and in 1982 and 1983 - second. In the future, French racers repeatedly managed to win prizes in redesigned sports versions of the Soviet "SUV".